<plot>Milo is your friendly neighborhood postman - with an unhealthy interest in your mail...and your life. "Milo" is a creepy-yet-romantic drama about a shy but vengeful postman who manipulates his control over the mail to win the love of a woman on his route. This strikingly bold Dark Romantic Thriller, asks the question: How much does your mailman really know about you?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?370252</url></doc>
